quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: "ganndal ɗum no ka Joomi am e ndeer Deftere, Joomi am majjataa o yejjitataa"."
  20,53,"Oon baɗanɗo on leydi ndi weƴƴitaandi, o naadani on e ndeer mayri laabi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngu ndiyam Min njaltiniri ɗam nooneeji immorde e puɗi ceertuɗi."
  20,54,"Ñaamee ngaynon neemoraaɗi mo'on ɗi. Pellet, no e ndeer ɗum [ko jaŋtaa ɗoo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- ɓe kakkillaaji ɗin."
  20,55,"Ko immorde e mayri Min Tagi on, ko e ndeer mayri Min nduttata on, ko immorde e mayri kadi Min njaltinoyta on laawol goɗgol"
  20,56,"Gooŋɗii Min kolli mo aayeeje Amen ɗen kala majje, o jeddi i o salii."
  20,57,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "enee, a ar ka amen fii yo a njaltinir min ka leydi amen mbilewu maaɗa ngun aan Muusaa?""
  20,58,"Maa min ngaddane mbilewu yeru maggu, waɗ fodoore hakkunde amen e maaɗa hara men lunndataako nde wonaa an kadi [lunndotoo nde] e nokkuure fotondirnde."
  20,59,"[Muusaa] maaki: fodoore mooɗon nden ko ñande saɗɗugol ngol, yo yimɓe ɓen mooɓindire mbeetaa(fenynyaange)."
  20,60,"Fir'awna ruŋiti o mooɓi pewje makko ɗen refti o ari."
  20,61,"Muusaa maakani ɓe: "On boniraama, wota on 'pekindo fenaande fawon e Alla sakko O mehira on Lepte, gooŋɗii sooyii on pekindiiɗo."
  20,62,"Ɓe pooɗondiri fiyaake maɓɓe on hakkunde maɓɓe, ɓe vuuɗi cowndi ɗin."
  20,63,"Ɓe mbi'i: "Pellet ɓee ɗiɗo ko wileeɓe heɓe paalaa yaltinirnde on ka leydi mon e mbilaaku maɓɓe ngu ɓe itta laawol mon ɓurngol l ngol."
  20,64,"Mooɓitee pewje mo'on ɗe refti ngaron ko on lappol, gooŋɗii malaama hannde on poolɗo."